message.body: Good morning. How are you?
Frazzled. Stupid alarm didn't go off
Oh no, are you late for anything?
No thankfully. I did have a meeting about 10 minutes after I got to the office though
Yikes! Rough start. Are you a bio-exorcist?
Um... wut?
Freelance. Like the movie
Freelance the movie? I know of freelance whales...
Not full time whales? Doing their own thing
Beetlejuice the movie
etting at
Ahhhh right. It just popped into my head when they asked for a username. But yea freelance whales is too hipster for me to have any idea what they were g
Yeah, they were just stringing words together. It's every hipsters dream to be a blue whale
Haha and fight the Japanese. So why Muggs?
It was a nickname a friend gave me a long time ago. No one uses it anymore so I thought I would bring it back. With strangers. In text form.
Hahaha well if you love it THAT much.... so what are you up to today muggsy?
Had a long sunny day. Just getting home and making a quick dinner now. How was your day?
Haha this conversation feels so similar to one I would have with someone I've known for a while. I wonder if this is how chat rooms became popular... tod
ay was fine, stayed busy at work so it didn't feel like an eternal day
I guess it's just nice to check in with someone. Good to hear work went well. Did you get to do anything for fun?

Have you had any significant others recently? Yea I went to dinner with some friends from my Bible study. I'm leaving my project after 9 months of beinghere every week so people are saying goodbye and stuff
I'm currently seeing someone, good guy. Dinner with friends sounds nice, where do you go now?
I've been going to Jersey for a while. Near new York though. I didn't think Muggs would be a girls nickname
Yep, I'm a lady. Did you eat in ny? I want to go to the rain room at the moma
Hmm never heard of the rain room. Sounds cool though. Haha we eat in jersey, tons of restaurants so it would be a waste to travel in
Are you getting crazy storms where you are?
No but I hear its bad back in Virginia. Where abouts are you?
Downpour just started, it's really dark. I had so many bike errands to run today...It's kind of nice to put my day on hold though
Do you only bike places?
I have a car, but I try to mostly bike. Parking is so frustrating in the city, I try to avoid it. Do you bike?
Yea I really like to bike when I can. I have a sweet road bike that I built myself. Only cost me $50. Do you not want to say which city you are in?
Wow, that's great. I'm in Philly, so center city is always under construction and the streets are terrible. Not to mention Ã¼ber aggressive drivers
So I have heard! My prof told me they saw someone hit 17 cars in on accident. Also, nice use of the umlaut
